userdoc.notice: Abstract reusable contract into template and deploy them in small sizes `minimal proxy` and `beacon proxy`. This contract can receive a fee lower than the deploy cost, and registered addresses do not have to pay the fee. Beacon is managed in this contract, it can be useful if you need a scalable upgrade through the `beacon proxy`.
